g the superiority of DAGFM to deal with\nthe industrial scale data in CTR prediction task. Our implementation code is\navailable at: https://github.com/RUCAIBox/DAGFM.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 21 Nov 2022 03:09:42 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 22 Dec 2022 01:58:16 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-12-23"}
