 these beam-field phenomena are anticipated to have applications\nin interface characterization, particle rotation/manipulation and other\nnano-optical processes.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 21 Nov 2022 08:07:38 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-02-28"}
