 properties in external galaxies using\npolarimetry of highly-reddened SNe is promising, providing a great opportunity\nto study the universality of such non-MW-like dust grains in the universe.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 21 Nov 2022 13:08:07 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 23 Nov 2022 19:36:31 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-12-14"}
