 technique is applicable to other interferometric observatories, as SKA,\nLOFAR, VLBI, and VLTI.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 21 Nov 2022 13:50:35 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-11-22"}
